			<p>
				<m>X</m> es <m>B(8;0,8)</m>
			</p>    
			<me>P(X=6)=p(2)=\binom{8}{6} \cdot 0,8^8 \cdot 0,2^2=0,2936</me>
		</solution>
	</exercise>
   
